operations.name: Append to { variable }
operations.value:
///$tab Model
App:
FIRST 1
LOAD DISTINCT
    AppId,
 AppName,
    AppOwner,
    AppOwnerId,
'{$.inputs.'Scan Base Sheets Only'}' AS AppScanBaseSheetsOnly,
{$.TemplateVersion} AS AppTemplateVersion,
{$.GetAppInformation.metadata.static_byte_size} AS BaseRAMFootprint,
Capitalize('{$.SpaceType}') AS AppSpaceType,
Replace('{$.SpaceName}','<apostrophe>',Chr(39)) AS AppSpaceName,
{subtract: {date: 'now','U'},{$.StartTime}} AS AppScanDuration
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(AppId)>=1;

SpaceTypeMap:
MAPPING LOAD
 AppId,
    AppSpaceType
RESIDENT App;

MasterDimLink:
LOAD DISTINCT
   MasterDimId & '|' & MasterDimLocation AS _MasterDimKey,
   MasterDimId,
   MasterDimLocation
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterDimId)>=1;

MasterMeasureLink:
LOAD DISTINCT
   MasterMeasureId & '|' & MasterMeasureLocation AS _MasterMeasureKey,
   MasterMeasureId,
   MasterMeasureLocation
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterMeasureId)>=1;

ObjectLink:
LOAD DISTINCT
   ObjectId & '|' & ObjectLocation & '|' & ObjectExpression AS _ObjectKey,
   ObjectId,
   ObjectLocation,
   Replace(ObjectExpression,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS ObjectExpression
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(ObjectId)>=1;

BookmarkLink:
LOAD DISTINCT
   BookmarkId & '|' & BookmarkLocation & '|' & BookmarkTextSearch AS _BookmarkKey,
   BookmarkId,
   BookmarkLocation,
   Replace(BookmarkTextSearch,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS BookmarkTextSearch
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(BookmarkId)>=1;

SheetLink:
LOAD DISTINCT
   SheetId & '|' & SheetLocation AS _SheetKey,
   SheetId,
   SheetLocation
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(SheetId)>=1;

JOIN (Data)
LOAD DISTINCT
  FieldName & '|' & FieldMatchStrength AS _FieldKeyVariable,
    VariableId
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(VariableId)>=1 AND Len(FieldName)>=1;

JOIN (Data)
LOAD DISTINCT
    FieldName & '|' & FieldMatchStrength AS _FieldKeyDim,
    MasterDimId
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterDimId)>=1 AND Len(FieldName)>=1;

JOIN (Data)
LOAD DISTINCT
    FieldName & '|' & FieldMatchStrength AS _FieldKeyMeasure,
    MasterMeasureId
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterMeasureId)>=1 AND Len(FieldName)>=1;

JOIN (Data)
LOAD DISTINCT
  FieldName & '|' & FieldMatchStrength AS _FieldKeyBookmark,
    BookmarkId
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(BookmarkId)>=1 AND Len(FieldName)>=1;

Bookmarks:
LOAD DISTINCT
    BookmarkId,
    BookmarkOwner,
    Capitalize(BookmarkPublished) AS BookmarkPublished,
    Capitalize(BookmarkApproved) AS BookmarkApproved,
    1 AS BookmarkCounter
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(BookmarkId)>=1;

MasterObjects:
LOAD DISTINCT
    MasterObjectId,
    Replace(MasterObjectName,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterObjectName,
    Replace(MasterObjectLabel,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterObjectLabel,
    Replace(MasterObjectDescription,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterObjectDescription,
    1 AS MasterObjectCounter
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterObjectId)>=1;

VariableCreatedInScriptMap:
MAPPING LOAD DISTINCT
  VariableId,
    Sign(Sum(Pick(Match(VariableCreatedInScript,'true'),1))) AS InScript
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(VariableId)>=1
GROUP BY VariableId;

Variables:
LOAD DISTINCT
    VariableId,
  If(ApplyMap('VariableCreatedInScriptMap',VariableId)=1,'True','False') AS VariableCreatedInScript,
    VariableName,
    Replace(VariableExpression,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS VariableExpression,
    1 AS VariableCounter
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(VariableId)>=1;

VariableNameMap:
MAPPING LOAD DISTINCT
 VariableId,
    VariableName
RESIDENT Variables
WHERE Len(VariableId)>0;

VariableReferences:
LOAD DISTINCT
 VariableId,
    VariableReferencedInVariableId,
    ApplyMap('VariableNameMap',VariableReferencedInVariableId) AS VariableReferencedInVariableName
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(VariableReferencedInVariableId)>0;

MasterDimensions:
LOAD DISTINCT
    MasterDimId,
    Replace(MasterDimTitle,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterDimTitle,
    Replace(MasterDimLabel,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterDimLabel,
    Replace(MasterDimDescription,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterDimDescription,
    1 AS MasterDimCounter
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterDimId)>=1;

MasterMeasures:
LOAD DISTINCT
   MasterMeasureId,
    Replace(MasterMeasureTitle,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterMeasureTitle,
    Replace(MasterMeasureLabel,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterMeasureLabel,
    Replace(MasterMeasureExpression,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterMeasureExpression,
  Replace(MasterMeasureDescription,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS MasterMeasureDescription,
  1 AS MasterMeasureCounter
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(MasterMeasureId)>=1;

Objects:
LOAD
DISTINCT 
    ObjectId,
    Replace(ObjectName,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS ObjectName,
    ObjectType,
    1 AS ObjectCounter
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(ObjectId)>=1;

ObjectNameMap:
MAPPING LOAD DISTINCT
 ObjectId,
    If(Len(ObjectName)>=1,ObjectName,'<NO OBJECT NAME>') AS ObjectName
RESIDENT Data;

ObjectTypeMap:
MAPPING LOAD DISTINCT
 ObjectId,
    ObjectType
RESIDENT Data;

ObjectRelationships:
LOAD DISTINCT
 ObjectId,
    ParentKey,
    ParentOrChild,
    ApplyMap('ObjectNameMap',ParentKey) AS ParentObjectName,
    ApplyMap('ObjectNameMap',ObjectId) AS ChildObjectName,
    ApplyMap('ObjectTypeMap',ParentKey) AS ParentObjectType,
    ApplyMap('ObjectTypeMap',ObjectId) AS ChildObjectType
RESIDENT Data;

Sheets:
LOAD
DISTINCT 
    SheetId,
    SheetOwner,
    SheetOwnerId,
    Replace(SheetName,'\newline',Chr(10)) AS SheetName,
    Capitalize(SheetPublished) AS SheetPublished,
    Capitalize(SheetApproved) AS SheetApproved,
    1 AS SheetCounter,
    If(SheetPublished='true',
     (If(SheetApproved='false',If(ApplyMap('SpaceTypeMap',AppId)='Managed','Community','Base'),'Base')),
        'Private') AS SheetType
RESIDENT Data
WHERE Len(SheetId)>=1;

RENAME TABLE Data TO TEMP;

Data:
LOAD DISTINCT
    _ObjectKey,
    _MasterDimKey,
    _MasterMeasureKey,
    _BookmarkKey,
    _SheetKey,
    MasterObjectId,
    VariableId,
    VariableMatchStrength,
    Subfield(RangeMaxString(_FieldKey,_FieldKeyDim,_FieldKeyMeasure,_FieldKeyVariable,_FieldKeyBookmark),'|',1) AS FieldName,
    If(Len(FieldMatchStrength)>=1,
     Subfield(RangeMaxString(_FieldKey,_FieldKeyDim,_FieldKeyMeasure,_FieldKeyVariable,_FieldKeyBookmark),'|',2)) AS FieldMatchStrength,
    If(Len(BookmarkId)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS BookmarkContainsField,
    If(Len(BookmarkId)>0 AND Len(VariableMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS BookmarkContainsVariable,
    If(Len(MasterDimId)>0 AND Len(MasterDimLocation)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS MasterDimContainsField,
    If(Len(MasterDimId)>0 AND Len(MasterDimLocation)>0 AND Len(VariableMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS MasterDimContainsVariable,
    If(Len(MasterMeasureId)>0 AND Len(MasterMeasureLocation)>0 AND Len(VariableMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS MasterMeasureContainsVariable,
    If(Len(MasterMeasureId)>0 AND Len(MasterMeasureLocation)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS MasterMeasureContainsField,
    If(Len(ObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS ObjectContainsField,
    If(Len(ObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(VariableMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS ObjectContainsVariable,
    If(Len(ObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(MasterDimId)>0,1,0) AS ObjectContainsMasterDim,
    If(Len(ObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(MasterMeasureId)>0,1,0) AS ObjectContainsMasterMeasure,
    If(Len(VariableId)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS VariableContainsField,
    If(Len(MasterObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS MasterObjectContainsField,
    If(Len(MasterObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(VariableMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS MasterObjectContainsVariable,
    If(Len(MasterObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(MasterDimId)>0,1,0) AS MasterObjectContainsMasterDim,
    If(Len(MasterObjectId)>0 AND Len(ObjectLocation)>0 AND Len(MasterMeasureId)>0,1,0) AS MasterObjectContainsMasterMeasure,
    If(Len(SheetLocation)>0 AND Len(FieldMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS SheetInfoContainsField,
    If(Len(SheetLocation)>0 AND Len(VariableMatchStrength)>0,1,0) AS SheetInfoContainsVariable
RESIDENT TEMP;

DROP TABLE TEMP;

FieldIsUsedMap:
MAPPING LOAD DISTINCT
   FieldName,
    1
RESIDENT Fields
WHERE FieldIsUsed='True';

VariableIsUsed:
LEFT JOIN(Variables)
LOAD DISTINCT
 VariableId,
    If(
     ApplyMap('VariableCreatedInScriptMap',VariableId)=1,'True',
        Pick(
         Match(
                Sign(
                  ObjectContainsVariable + 
                  MasterDimContainsVariable + 
                  MasterMeasureContainsVariable + 
                  MasterObjectContainsVariable + 
                  BookmarkContainsVariable
   ),1
        ,0),'True','False')
    ) AS VariableIsUsed
;
LOAD DISTINCT
 VariableId,
    Sign(Sum(ObjectContainsVariable)) AS ObjectContainsVariable,
    Sign(Sum(MasterDimContainsVariable)) AS MasterDimContainsVariable,
    Sign(Sum(MasterMeasureContainsVariable)) AS MasterMeasureContainsVariable,
    Sign(Sum(MasterObjectContainsVariable)) AS MasterObjectContainsVariable,
    Sign(Sum(BookmarkContainsVariable)) AS BookmarkContainsVariable
RESIDENT Data
GROUP BY VariableId;

LEFT JOIN (Fields)
LOAD
   FieldName,
  Pick(Match(Sign(Sum(If(FieldMatchStrength='Exact',1,0)))+1,1,2),'False','True') AS FieldExactMatchFound
RESIDENT Data
WHERE ApplyMap('FieldIsUsedMap',FieldName)=1
GROUP BY FieldName;

AUTONUMBER '_*';

blocks.name: customCode
blocks.comment: Calculate the per-Field RAM footprint.

inputs.value:
# Example code
import json
from math import log,ceil

fieldInfo = inputs['FieldInfo']
tableRows = fieldInfo['table_rows']
cardinality = fieldInfo['cardinality']
byteSize = fieldInfo['byte_size']

fieldBits = ceil(max(log(cardinality) / log(2), 1))
recordBytes = ceil(fieldBits * tableRows / 8)
totalRAMbytes = recordBytes + byteSize + cardinality

fieldInfo['record_bytes'] = recordBytes
fieldInfo['total_RAM_bytes'] = totalRAMbytes
fieldInfo['total_RAM_MB'] = round(totalRAMbytes / 1024 / 1024,2)

print(json.dumps(fieldInfo))
